<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Pablo Elias | UIUX Designer</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fira+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/lucide@latest"></script>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Fira Sans', sans-serif;
            background-color: #0d0f1a;
            color: #FFFFFF;
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
        }
        h1 { font-size: 48px; font-weight: 500; }
        h2 { font-size: 80px; font-weight: 500; }
        h3 { font-size: 32px; font-weight: 500; }
        h4 { font-size: 28px; font-weight: 500; }
        
        .bg-accent { background-color: #E50914; }
        .text-accent { color: #E50914; }
        
        /* New Project Grid Styles */
        .project-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-cols: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(424px, 1fr));
            gap: 40px;
            justify-items: center;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 40px 0;
        }

        .project-card-wrapper {
            width: 466px;
            height: 360px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .project-card {
            width: 424px;
            height: 328px;
            position: relative;
            border-radius: 32px;
            overflow: hidden;
            transition: all 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
            cursor: pointer;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
        }

        .project-card:hover {
            width: 466px;
            height: 360px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
        }

        .project-card img {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            object-fit: cover;
            transition: opacity 0.5s ease;
        }

        .project-card img.hover-img {
            opacity: 0;
        }

        .project-card:hover img.default-img {
            opacity: 0;
        }

        .project-card:hover img.hover-img {
            opacity: 1;
        }

        @media (max-width: 500px) {
            .project-card-wrapper {
                width: 100%;
                height: auto;
                aspect-ratio: 424/328;
            }
            .project-card {
                width: 100%;
                height: 100%;
            }
            .project-card:hover {
                width: 100%;
                height: 100%;
                transform: scale(1.05);
            }
        }

        /* Carousel Fixed Height */
        .carousel-container {
            position: relative;
            width: 100%;
            height: 500px;
        }

        .carousel-item {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0; left: 0;
            width: 100%; height: 100%;
            opacity: 0;
            visibility: hidden;
            transition: opacity 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
            z-index: 10;
        }

        .carousel-item img {
            width: 100%; height: 100%;
            object-fit: contain;
            border-radius: 1rem;
        }

        .carousel-item.active {
            position: absolute;
            opacity: 1;
            visibility: visible;
            z-index: 30;
        }

        /* Parallax Background Elements */
        .parallax-bg {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            pointer-events: none;
            z-index: -1;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .bg-element-1 {
            position: absolute;
            top: -10%;
            right: -10%;
            width: 80%;
            max-width: 1000px;
            opacity: 0.4;
            filter: blur(60px);
            animation: float-bg 20s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        .bg-element-2 {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -10%;
            left: -10%;
            width: 70%;
            max-width: 900px;
            opacity: 0.3;
            filter: blur(80px);
            animation: float-bg 25s ease-in-out infinite reverse;
        }

        @keyframes float-bg {
            0%, 100% { transform: translate(0, 0) rotate(0deg); }
            33% { transform: translate(5%, 5%) rotate(5deg); }
            66% { transform: translate(-5%, 2%) rotate(-3deg); }
        }

        .slide-html {
            background-color: #1a1d2e;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
        }

        /* Expanded Details Animation */
        .details-container {
            max-height: 0;
            overflow: hidden;
            transition: max-height 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
        }
        .details-container.open {
            max-height: 10000px;
        }

        .skill-card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
        }

        .skill-card:hover {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            border-color: rgba(229, 9, 20, 0.3);
            transform: translateY(-8px);
        }

        /* Icon Animations */
        @keyframes icon-float {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
            50% { transform: translateY(-5px); }
        }

        .lucide {
            transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
        }

        h2 .lucide, h3 .lucide {
            animation: icon-float 3s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        .skill-card:hover .lucide {
            transform: scale(1.2) rotate(12deg);
            filter: drop-shadow(0 0 8px rgba(229, 9, 20, 0.5));
        }

        a:hover .lucide, button:hover .lucide {
            transform: translateX(4px);
        }
        /* Floating Navbar Style */
        #navbar {
            transition: all 0.5s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
            width: 100%;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
        }

        #navbar.nav-scrolled {
            top: 24px;
            width: auto;
            min-width: min(90%, 1000px);
            background: rgba(13, 15, 26, 0.7);
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border-radius: 999px;
            padding: 16px 96px !important;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
        }

        #navbar.nav-scrolled .brand-name {
            color: #E8172C;
        }

        #navbar.nav-scrolled .nav-link {
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            #navbar.nav-scrolled {
                padding: 12px 24px !important;
                min-width: 90%;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="overflow-x-hidden bg-[#0d0f1a]">

    <!-- Parallax Background Elements -->
    <div class="parallax-bg">
        <img src="assets/ellipse-bg.png" alt="" class="bg-element-1">
        <img src="assets/group-bg.png" alt="" class="bg-element-2">
    </div>

    <!-- Navbar -->
    <nav id="navbar" class="fixed top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 z-50 bg-transparent px-6 py-4 md:px-12 border-b border-white/0 transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto flex justify-between items-center w-full">
            <a href="#" class="brand-name text-lg font-medium tracking-wider uppercase transition-colors duration-300">PABLO ELIAS</a>
            <div class="hidden md:flex items-center space-x-12 text-sm font-medium">
                <a href="#proyectos" class="nav-link hover:text-white transition text-white/60">Proyectos</a>
                <a href="#sobre-mi" class="nav-link hover:text-white transition text-white/60">Sobre mí</a>
                <a href="#contacto" class="nav-link border border-white/20 px-6 py-2 rounded-full hover:bg-white hover:text-black transition">Contacto</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="relative min-h-screen bg-transparent pt-4 pb-20 px-6 overflow-hidden">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto w-full relative min-h-[950px]">
            <div class="relative z-10 mt-4 mx-auto md:ml-[5%] lg:ml-[8%] w-full max-w-[850px] md:w-[850px] h-auto rounded-[24px] overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
                <img src="assets/img-hero.png" alt="Pablo Elias Hero" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
            </div>

            <!-- Hero Stats -->
            <div class="mt-12 md:ml-[8%] max-w-[850px] grid grid-cols-3 gap-8 text-left">
                <div class="space-y-1 hero-stat transition-transform hover:scale-105 cursor-default">
                    <p class="text-4xl font-medium text-white tracking-tighter uppercase">+4</p>
                    <p class="text-[10px] md:text-xs font-medium text-white/40 uppercase tracking-widest leading-tight">
                        Años de<br>experiencia
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="space-y-1 hero-stat transition-transform hover:scale-105 cursor-default">
                    <p class="text-4xl font-medium text-white tracking-tighter uppercase">+20</p>
                    <p class="text-[10px] md:text-xs font-medium text-white/40 uppercase tracking-widest leading-tight">
                        Proyectos<br>completados
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="space-y-1 hero-stat transition-transform hover:scale-105 cursor-default">
                    <p class="text-4xl font-medium text-white tracking-tighter uppercase">+15</p>
                    <p class="text-[10px] md:text-xs font-medium text-white/40 uppercase tracking-widest leading-tight">
                        Clientes<br>satisfechos
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="absolute top-[380px] left-0 -translate-y-1/2 z-20 pointer-events-none hidden md:flex items-center ml-[calc(8%-100px)]">
                <div class="text-[160px] font-medium uppercase leading-none tracking-tighter flex">
                    <span class="text-white">UI</span>
                    <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-white from-50% to-[#E50914] to-50% bg-clip-text text-transparent">U</span>
                    <span class="text-[#E50914]">X</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="relative md:absolute md:top-10 md:right-[2%] lg:right-[5%] z-40 w-full md:max-w-[450px] md:h-[900px] mt-12 md:mt-0 flex flex-col items-start md:items-end">
                <div class="absolute top-[280px] -right-[150px] text-[160px] font-medium uppercase leading-none tracking-tighter flex pointer-events-none">
                    <span class="text-[#E50914]">DE</span>
                    <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-[#E50914] from-50% to-white to-50% bg-clip-text text-transparent">S</span>
                    <span class="text-white">IGNER</span>
                </div>
                
                <div class="absolute bottom-0 flex flex-col items-start md:items-end gap-6 w-full">
                    <div class="space-y-1">
                        <h2 class="text-[32px] font-medium text-white uppercase leading-none">HOLA,</h2>
                        <h2 class="text-[32px] font-medium text-white uppercase leading-none">
                            SOY <span class="text-[#E50914]">PABLO ELIAS</span>
                        </h2>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-white/60 text-base leading-relaxed text-left md:text-right max-w-sm font-normal">
                        Diseñador de experiencias y productos digitales orientados a usuarios y métricas. Especializado en crear soluciones visuales que conectan marcas con personas de manera intuitiva y funcional.
                    </p>
                    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-4 w-full md:w-auto justify-end">
                        <a href="#proyectos" class="bg-[#E50914] text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full text-sm font-medium hover:scale-105 transition shadow-lg flex items-center justify-center space-x-2">
                            <span>Ver Proyectos</span>
                        </a>
                        <a href="#" class="border border-white/20 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full text-sm font-medium hover:bg-white hover:text-black transition flex items-center justify-center space-x-2">
                            <span>Descargar CV</span>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Proyectos Section -->
    <section id="proyectos" class="py-24 px-6 bg-transparent relative z-10">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
            <h2 class="uppercase tracking-tighter mb-24 text-white text-8xl font-medium"><i data-lucide="folder-kanban" class="w-12 h-12 text-accent inline-block mr-4 align-middle"></i>PROYECTOS</h2>
            
            <div class="flex flex-col gap-32">
                <!-- Project 1: AguaLuz -->
                <div class="rounded-[40px] overflow-hidden flex flex-col bg-[#1a1d2e] relative transition-all duration-500">
                    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row relative">
                        <div class="absolute top-10 right-10 w-[80px] h-[80px] z-40">
                            <img src="assets/agualuz/logo.png" alt="AguaLuz Logo" class="w-full h-full object-contain">
                        </div>
                        <div class="md:w-[45%] flex flex-col p-10 md:p-20 md:pb-20">
                            <div class="mb-12"><span class="inline-block bg-black/40 text-white/80 px-4 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-wider">UI/UX</span></div>
                            <div class="flex-grow flex flex-col justify-center">
                                <h3 class="text-6xl md:text-[72px] font-medium text-white mb-6 leading-none tracking-tighter uppercase">AGUALUZ</h3>
                                <p class="text-[18px] text-white/60 leading-relaxed max-w-[400px] font-normal">Sistema SaaS para la gestión operativa y administración de distribución de agua potable.</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="mt-12 space-y-6">
                                <p class="text-white/40 text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-widest font-normal">¿Deseas saber mas de este proyecto?</p>
                                <button id="toggle-agualuz" class="bg-[#E8172C] text-white px-10 py-5 rounded-full text-sm font-medium flex items-center space-x-3 hover:scale-105 transition w-fit group">
                                    <span class="btn-text">Ver detalles</span>
                                    <i data-lucide="chevron-down" class="w-5 h-5 transition-transform duration-500 group-[.open]:rotate-180"></i>
                                </button>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="md:w-[55%] flex items-center justify-center p-10 md:p-20 md:pb-20">
                            <div id="agualuz-carousel" class="carousel-container">
                                <div class="carousel-item active" data-index="0"><img src="assets/agualuz/screen-01.png"></div>
                                <div class="carousel-item" data-index="1"><img src="assets/agualuz/screensgroup.png"></div>
                                <div class="carousel-item" data-index="2"><img src="assets/agualuz/mobile.png"></div>
                                <div class="carousel-item slide-html w-full rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-10 flex flex-col justify-between" data-index="3">
                                    <div class="w-full space-y-4">
                                        <div class="space-y-1">
                                            <h4 class="text-2xl font-medium text-white uppercase tracking-tight">¿TIENES PREGUNTAS?</h4>
                                            <p class="text-white/60 text-xs font-normal leading-relaxed">Si tienes dudas y quieres saber más, para mi es un gusto hablar sobre proyectos. Dime que tienes en mente.</p>
                                        </div>
                                        
                                        <div class="space-y-3">
                                            <div class="space-y-1">
                                                <label class="text-[10px] font-medium text-white/40 uppercase tracking-widest ml-1">Mail</label>
                                                <input type="email" placeholder="Ingrese su mail" class="w-full bg-transparent border border-white/10 rounded-[18px] px-5 py-3 text-sm text-white placeholder:text-white/20 outline-none focus:border-white/30 transition-all">
                                            </div>
                                            
                                            <div class="space-y-1">
                                                <label class="text-[10px] font-medium text-white/40 uppercase tracking-widest ml-1">Message</label>
                                                <div class="relative bg-transparent border border-white/10 rounded-[18px] overflow-hidden focus-within:border-white/30 transition-all">
                                                    <textarea placeholder="Cuentame tus ideas..." class="w-full bg-transparent px-5 py-4 text-sm text-white placeholder:text-white/20 outline-none resize-none h-24"></textarea>
                                                    <button class="absolute bottom-3 right-5 flex items-center gap-2 group transition-all hover:scale-105">
                                                         <i data-lucide="send-horizontal" class="w-4 h-4 text-white/40 group-hover:text-white transition-colors"></i>
                                                         <span class="text-sm font-medium text-white/40 group-hover:text-white transition-colors">Enviar</span>
                                                    </button>
                                                </div>
                                                <p class="text-[8px] text-white/20 ml-2">Máx 100 caracteres</p>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <p class="text-white font-medium text-[10px] uppercase tracking-wider text-left w-full border-t border-white/5 pt-4">Mientras tanto puedes revisar los detalles de este proyecto</p>
                                </div>
                                <button id="next-agualuz" class="absolute right-0 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 z-50 bg-white/10 hover:bg-[#E8172C] backdrop-blur-md w-14 h-14 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center border border-white/20 transition-all"><i data-lucide="chevron-right" class="text-white w-7 h-7"></i></button>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div id="agualuz-details" class="details-container bg-[#1a1d2e]">
                        <div class="px-10 md:px-20 pb-20 space-y-[80px] border-t border-white/5 pt-20">
                            <!-- DESCRIPCIÓN -->
                            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-16">
                                <div class="md:w-1/2 space-y-8">
                                    <h4 class="text-[56px] font-normal text-white uppercase tracking-tighter leading-tight">DESCRIPCIÓN DEL PROYECTO</h4>
                                    <p class="text-lg text-white/60 leading-relaxed font-normal">Empresa de distribución de bidones que gestionaba pedidos mediante WhatsApp, llamadas y registros manuales. No existía un sistema centralizado para administrar clientes, rutas ni conductores.</p>
                                </div>
                                <div class="md:w-1/2"><img src="assets/agualuz/web.png" class="w-full rounded-3xl shadow-2xl"></div>
                            </div>

                            <!-- OBJETIVO -->
                            <div class="space-y-12">
                                <h4 class="text-[56px] font-normal text-white uppercase tracking-tighter leading-tight">OBJETIVO</h4>
                                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-16">
                                    <p class="text-lg text-white/60 leading-relaxed font-normal">Diseñar desde cero un sistema que digitalizara y organizara la operación completa entre oficina y conductores.</p>
                                    <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
                                        <img src="assets/agualuz/web.png" class="w-full rounded-2xl shadow-xl">
                                        <p class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-white/40 text-center font-normal">Visualización de la saas</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <!-- MI ROL -->
                            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-16">
                                <div class="md:w-1/2 space-y-8">
                                    <h4 class="text-[56px] font-normal text-white uppercase tracking-tighter leading-tight">MI ROL</h4>
                                    <p class="text-lg text-white/60 leading-relaxed font-normal">Lideré el diseño de UX/UI, definiendo la arquitectura del sistema, flujos principales y diseño de interfaz, trabajando en conjunto con desarrollo y el cliente durante las iteraciones.</p>
                                </div>
                                <div class="md:w-1/2"><img src="assets/agualuz/screens.png" class="w-full rounded-3xl shadow-2xl"></div>
                            </div>

                            <!-- ARQUITECTURA -->
                            <div class="space-y-12">
                                <h4 class="text-[56px] font-normal text-white uppercase tracking-tighter leading-tight">ARQUITECTURA</h4>
                                <p class="text-lg text-white/60 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl font-normal">Diseñé un mapa estructural previo que organizaba módulos, roles y flujos para asegurar escalabilidad y coherencia entre ambas plataformas.</p>
                                <img src="assets/agualuz/arquitectura.png" class="w-full rounded-3xl shadow-2xl">
                            </div>

                            <!-- PROBLEMA -->
                            <div class="space-y-12 border-t border-white/5 pt-20">
                                <h4 class="text-[56px] font-normal text-white uppercase tracking-tighter leading-tight">PROBLEMA</h4>
                                <ul class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-x-16 gap-y-6 text-white/60 text-lg font-normal">
                                    <li class="flex items-start space-x-3"><span class="text-[#E8172C]">•</span> <span>Pedidos manuales y desorganizados</span></li>
                                    <li class="flex items-start space-x-3"><span class="text-[#E8172C]">•</span> <span>Falta de visibilidad sobre rutas y estados</span></li>
                                    <li class="flex items-start space-x-3"><span class="text-[#E8172C]">•</span> <span>Sistema de registros de llamadas antiguo</span></li>
                                    <li class="flex items-start space-x-3"><span class="text-[#E8172C]">•</span> <span>Comunicación informal entre oficina y choferes</span></li>
                                    <li class="flex items-start space-x-3"><span class="text-[#E8172C]">•</span> <span>Información de clientes dispersa</span></li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>

                            <!-- SOLUCIÓN -->
                            <div class="space-y-12 border-t border-white/5 pt-20">
                                <h4 class="text-[56px] font-normal text-white uppercase tracking-tighter leading-tight">SOLUCIÓN</h4>
                                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-16">
                                    <div class="space-y-8">
                                        <h5 class="text-2xl font-normal text-white uppercase">App Web (operadores)</h5>
                                        <p class="text-white/60 text-lg font-normal">Identificación automática de clientes, gestión de pedidos y visualización de conductores en mapa en tiempo real.</p>
                                        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6">
                                            <img src="assets/agualuz/web.png" class="w-full rounded-2xl shadow-xl">
                                            <img src="assets/agualuz/Creacion de rutas 3.png" class="w-full rounded-2xl shadow-xl">
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="space-y-8">
                                        <h5 class="text-2xl font-normal text-white uppercase">App Móvil (conductores)</h5>
                                        <p class="text-white/60 text-lg font-normal">Actualización de estado de pedidos, carga de datos de clientes y canal de chat directo con la oficina.</p>
                                        <img src="assets/agualuz/mobile.png" class="w-full rounded-2xl shadow-xl">
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <!-- ITERACIÓN -->
                            <div class="space-y-12 border-t border-white/5 pt-20">
                                <h4 class="text-[56px] font-normal text-white uppercase tracking-tighter leading-tight">ITERACIÓN</h4>
                                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
                                    <p class="text-lg text-white/60 leading-relaxed font-normal">Probamos y ajustamos el flujo de creación de rutas para que fuera lo más automatizado posible, reduciendo el tiempo de despacho en un 40%.</p>
                                    <img src="assets/agualuz/automatización 1.png" class="w-full rounded-3xl shadow-2xl">
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <!-- RESULTADO -->
                            <div class="space-y-12 border-t border-white/5 pt-20">
                                <h4 class="text-[56px] font-normal text-white uppercase tracking-tighter leading-tight">RESULTADO</h4>
                                <p class="text-lg text-white/60 leading-relaxed max-w-3xl font-normal">Se logró un sistema integral que no solo digitalizó la operación, sino que permitió a la empresa escalar su volumen de pedidos sin necesidad de contratar más personal administrativo.</p>
                                <img src="assets/agualuz/screens2.png" class="w-full rounded-3xl shadow-2xl">
                            </div>

